Where should we start?

00:01:59.090 --> 00:02:03.390
Well, perhaps it will make you feel better if I congratulated

00:02:03.390 --> 00:02:07.780
you for taking on the difficult task of learning English.

00:02:08.760 --> 00:02:09.190
Why?

00:02:09.760 --> 00:02:15.210
Well, firstly, this curious language has so many words in its vocabulary.

